  <summary date="2023-09-28T19:15:19Z" status="Introduced in House">Restroom Access Act of 2023

This bill requires retailers to allow a customer to use a nonpublic restroom if the customer has an eligible medical condition (e.g., inflammatory bowel disease) that requires immediate access to a restroom and other conditions are met.</summary>
